  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective is to show the impact on the quality of life (QoL) for adults patients&#xD;
      with advanced cancer managed in day hospital of integrated palliative care of cancer center&#xD;
      (HDJ-SPI).&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
