  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Analyse impact of hospital day care in integrated palliative care department on quality of life of adult patients with advanced stage cancer</measure>
    <time_frame>12 months</time_frame>
    <description>Analyse impact of hospital day care in integrated palliative care department on quality of life of adult patients with advanced stage cancer&#xD;
Outcome shall be evaluated by assessing Survival without quality of life deterioration,measured by EORTC QLQ-C30 scale with monthly evaluation targeting three dimensions :&#xD;
